{
  "design_notes": "S0 introduces the rhythm with a clean, low-density progression starting at Bar 1 to let players settle into the tempo. S1 leverages a continuous stream of integer-beat taps mapping the driving synthwave kicks directly to the center BAR lane, while the melodies alternate outer lanes in a shifting left-to-right wave motion that changes direction every bar. S2 maintains the rhythmic flow while easing the player through the outro with the same smooth alternating pattern, ensuring a satisfying and physically balanced end to the track.",
